<span weight='bold' size='xx-large'>Email</span>

The <b>Email</b> of a <b>Contact</b> isn't required for entry,
but when it is entered, the only certain formats are allowed.

For example, the following are <b>good</b>:

email@email.com
email@email.com.uk
email@email.com.au
email@email.org
name.last@email.com

And the following are <b>bad</b>:

email@@email.com
email.com
email@email.com extra
